'''薩皮埃哈宮'''（{{lang-pl|pałac Sapiehów w Warszawie}}）是位於[[波蘭|波蘭]][[華沙|華沙]][[華沙新城區|新城區]]的一座建築。現在這座建築由波蘭環境保護學院使用<ref name="warszawa1939">{{cite news |author =  |url = http://www.warszawa1939.pl/index.php?r1=zakroczymska_6&r3=0 |title = Pałac Sapiehów |work = www.warszawa1939.pl |publisher =  |pages =  |page =  |date =  |accessdate = 2009-03-23 |archive-date = 2016-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194113/http://www.warszawa1939.pl/index.php?r1=zakroczymska_6&r3=0 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。薩皮埃哈宮建築外觀為[[洛可可|洛可可]]式風格，修建於1731年至1746年期間<ref name="perelki">{{cite news  |author =  |url = http://um.warszawa.pl/v_syrenka/perelki/index_en.php?mi_id=65&dz_id=3 |title = The Sapieha Palace |work = eGuide / Treasures of Warsaw on-line |publisher =  |pages =  |page =  |date = |accessdate = 2009-03-23}}</ref>。二戰期間薩皮埃哈宮被德軍摧毀。在1950年代薩皮埃哈宮得到重建。

